flowchart TD
    Start([Slice marked competitive]) --> Spawn{Spawn worktrees}
    Spawn -->|Strategy A| WTA[.forge/worktrees/A/]
    Spawn -->|Strategy B| WTB[.forge/worktrees/B/]
    WTA --> GateA[Run validation gate]
    WTB --> GateB[Run validation gate]
    GateA --> RevA[Invoke reviewer<br/>if innerLoop.reviewer.enabled]
    GateB --> RevB[Invoke reviewer<br/>if innerLoop.reviewer.enabled]
    RevA --> Elect{Winner election}
    RevB --> Elect
    Elect -->|Gate pass + best reviewer score| Winner[Promote winner to working tree]
    Elect -->|Tie on gate + reviewer| Cost[Token-cost tie-breaker]
    Cost --> Winner
    Winner --> Cleanup[Clean up losing worktrees]
    Cleanup --> Done([Slice committed])
    GateA -.gate fail.-> AutoFix{Auto-fix proposal?}
    GateB -.gate fail.-> AutoFix
    AutoFix -->|Small, local diff| Patch[Write .forge/proposed-fixes/*.patch]
    AutoFix -->|Complex| Skip[Record in postmortem]
